  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Have an undiagnosed suspicious solid or mostly solid thyroid nodule

          -  Have received recommendation for and are scheduled for biopsy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous or on-going radioactive iodine treatment.

          -  Have greater than 2 nodules (1 in each lobe) recommended for biopsy at baseline

          -  Previous biopsy of target nodule
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
